org.hps.monitoring.ecal.eventdisplay.event

Class EcalHit

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.monitoring.ecal.eventdisplay.event.EcalHit

  • public final class EcalHit
extends Object
    The class EcalHit is an extension of Datum that stores an energy. This is used for reading input from a text file. CalorimeterHit should be used when reading from an LCIO file.
